 Health and wellness Retail store and if you take a good look, you will witness that they promote a fairly substantial series of CBD items, primarily CBD oil and they also happen to take PayPal as a settlement method. It appears that PayPal is administering twos sets of rules to many different firms. As a result of this restriction, I can no longer accept PayPal on my CBD-related site. This has limited my payment possibilities and presently, I am heavily dependent on Cryptocurrency payments and straightforward bank transfers. I have gotten in touch with a solicitor from a Magic Circle law firm in The city of london and they said that what PayPal is doing is altogether not legal and discriminatory as it ought to be applying a consistent benchmark to all firms. I am yet to speak to yet another attorney from a US law practice in London to see what PayPal\\\'s legal position is in the USA. Meanwhile, I would be highly appreciative if anyone here at targetdomain could offer me with substitute payment processors/merchants that work with CBD companies.',0,'post-trashed','','comment',0,0),(6,2167,'Felisa','support@modapharma.com','https://images.google.com.tw/url?q=https://www.skinaestheticlinic.com/3-tricks-to-clean-your-e-mail-record-and-hold-engagement-high/','147.78.141.85','2021-12-12 19:15:35','2021-12-12 19:15:35','can i vape hash',0,'post-trashed','','comment',0,0),(7,2167,'project runway guy who makes ugly pink lingerie','merakiwelivelikethis@gmail.com','https://lkazka.com.ua/user/thumbchef2624/','147.78.141.85','2022-01-17 08:14:30','2022-01-17 08:14:30','Can someone recommend Sexy &amp; Seductive Styles? Thanks xxx',0,'post-trashed','','comment',0,0),(8,2167,'Good Vibes Vapor','rjisley@greenstar.coop','http://forum.mele.cn/user-79585.html','147.78.141.85','2022-01-27 02:22:21','2022-01-27 02:22:21','Does anyone have any idea A Clean Cigarette vaporizer store located in 4118 Central Ave. SE Suite D offers e-juice made by Juice Bomb eLiquids Made In UK E-liquid? I 