riting CSS)</li><li>Proficient in Photoshop, Illustrator, bonus points for familiarity with Sketch (Sketch is our preferred concepting tool)</li><li>Cross-browser and platform testing as standard practice</li><li>Experience using Invision a plus</li><li>Experience in video production a plus or, at a minimum, a willingness to learn</li></ul>\n\n<h4>Education + Experience</h4><ul><li>Advanced degree or equivalent experience in graphic and web design</li><li>3 or more years of professional design experience</li><li>Direct response email experience</li><li>Ecommerce website design experience</li></ul>','UX Designer','','publish','closed','closed','','ux-designer','','','2022-10-12 03:22:38','2022-10-12 03:22:38','',0,'https://demo.flawlessthemes.com/espyjobsfree/index.php/job/ux-designer/',0,'job_listing','',0),(21081,1,'2022-06-18 10:13:18','2022-06-18 10:13:18','','listing-hero-image-6','','inherit','open','closed','','listing-hero-image-6','','','2022-10-12 03:22:37','2022-10-12 03:22:37','',21080,'https://demo.flawlessthemes.com/espyjobsfree/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/listing-hero-image-6.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21082,1,'2022-06-18 10:13:22','2022-06-18 10:13:22','','listing-aol-logo','','inherit','open','closed','','listing-aol-logo','','','2022-10-12 03:22:37','2022-10-12 03:22:37','',21080,'https://demo.flawlessthemes.com/espyjobsfree/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/listing-aol-logo.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21083,1,'2022-06-18 10:13:26','2022-06-18 10:13:26','<img class=\'alignnone size-full\' src=\'http://wordpress.local/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/listing-hero-image-7.jpg\' width=\'1110\' height=\'342\' /><h4>Company Description</h4>\nCompany is a 2016 Iowa City-born start-up that develops consectetuer adipiscing elit. Phasellus hendrerit. Pellentesque aliquet nibh nec urna. In nisi neque, aliquet vel, dapibus id, mattis vel, nisi. Sed pretium, ligula sollicitudin laoreet viverra, tortor libero sodales leo, eget blandit nunc tortor eu nibh. N